ology are the best in the industry” the huycon product line offers tailormade solutions for all kinds of nonwoven spunbondmeltblown production processes and materials like pp pe pet bico and other newer polymers running at speeds over  meters per minute sophisticated weave structures combined with specific surface treatments guarantees maximum production efficiencies and excellent web properties  about xerium technologies xerium technologies inc xrm is a leading global provider of industrial consumable products and services xerium which operates around the world under a variety of brand names utilizes a broad portfolio of patented and proprietary technologies to provide customers with tailored solutions and products integral to production all designed to optimize performance and reduce operational costs with  manufacturing facilities in  countries around the world xerium has approximately  employees contact xerium technologies incsteve cole – director – global marketingstevecolexeriumcom     xerium technologies inc all rights reserved site developed by corpcomm group inc about us  terms  conditions  privacy policy for our north american customers  for our north amerian suppliers  employment ca supply chains act xerium celebrates shipment of th huycon process belt for nonwoven fabrics production from gloggnitz austria facility  leading technology in machine clothing roll covers and advanced dynamic nip analysis language  select  english spanish   한국어 french portuguese deutsch menu  homemarkets  productspulp  paper  tissueforming fabricspress feltsdryer fabricstissue tad fabricsroll coversspreader rollssmart® technologyshoe press beltsmechanical servicesfiber  stock processingnonwoven fabricsbuilding productsspecialty productsindustrial rollsnonwoven industrymetal industryfilm industrythe xerium differencenewsxerium newsin the mediaresourcesvideossustainabilitycontactcontact uslocationsemploymentinvestor relations xerium celebrates shipment of th huycon process belt f