technology at a time when bronze wires were the standard shortly after we then pioneered xweave extra shute product technology xerium also invented and introduced ssb class triple layer technology known as huytexx delivering unprecedented machine performance and sheet quality press felts xeriums ancestors manufactured metal wires and woolen press felts two centuries ago and quickly established an excellent reputation in the paper industry as a result of more demanding paper machines coming online in recent years xerium has set entirely new standards as the marketleading innovator in endless and seam felt technology   dryer fabrics xerium offers a wide variety of dryer fabrics for every position on the machine covering all paper grades  our woven styles are provided with pin seams or pinspiral seams to fit the position requirements in addition we offer an excellent portfolio of spiral dryer fabrics for those applications with special requirements  roll covers xeriums stowe woodward roll cover product portfolio includes premium performance rubber polyurethane and composite technology engineered specifically for each application our innovative products are the standard by which roll technology is measured   spreader rolls xeriums stowe and mount hope bowed spreader rolls products provide highperformance web and fabric smoothing for the most demanding applications in addition our portfolio includes all metal rolls as well as specially engineered sleeves for high temperature and high speed applications smart® technology xeriums roll product portfolio includes stowe roll covers stowe and mount hope bowed spreader rolls and smart® technology our roll cover products are engineered for each papermaking machine  our patented smart® technology uses embedded sensors in roll covers to dynamically measure nip conditions across numerous sections of the machine mechanical services xerium offers a full range of rollrelated repairs and upgrades from ontherun otr roll analysis vibration analysis internal inspection  repair optical  laser alignment suction box overhauls to new shell constructions and much more     xerium technologies inc all rights reserved site developed by corpcomm group inc about us  terms  conditions  privacy policy for our north american customers  for our north amerian suppliers  employment ca supply chains act xerium technologies inc  linkedin linkedin main content starts below xerium technologies  schedules second quarter  earnings conference call  traders log in email password remember forgot password  become a member for free sign up sign up new membersign up for free new customerdiscover our portfolios united states united kingdom france deutschland schweiz de suisse fr settings dynamic quotes  offon markets equities north americaeuropeasiaoceaniamiddle east� more equities indexes dow jonessp nasdaq tsx compftse � more indexes currency  forex eur  usdgbp  usdusd  jpyusd  cadaud  usd� more currencies commodities goldcrude oil wticrude oil brentsilverplatinum� more commodities news latest news companiesmarketseconomycurrency  forexcommoditiesinterest ratesbusiness leadersfinancial calendareconomic calendar listed company analyst recorumorsiposcapital markets transactionsnew contractsprofits warningsappointmentspress releaseseventscorporate actions sector news energybasic materialsindustrialsconsumer cyclicalconsumer noncyclicalfinancialshealthcaretechnologytelecommunications servicesutilities analysis all analysiscommentariesindex analysisstock trading strategiescommodity analysisforex analysis stock picks all stock picks portfolios my portfolio virtual portfolios traders portfolios european portfoliousa portfolioasian portfolio screeners market screener homefundamental analyse top investor ratingtop trading ratingtop consensusgrowth stocksyield stockslow valuations technical analysis oversold stocksoverbought stocksclose to resistancesclose to supportsaccumulation phasemost volatile stocks watchlists my watchlists watch