timize the performance of their equipment and reduce the costs of their operations xrm is a global enterprise selling to customers in  countries with  manufacturing facilities in  countries and approximately  employeesview source version on businesswirecom httpwwwbusinesswirecomnewshomeenreblogsharetweetsharerecently viewedyour list is emptywhat to read nextthe pizzamaking robots that want to change the worldyahoo financewhy it might be ‘dangerous’ for ibm to turn itself around professoryahoo financeoj simpson owes millions heres why he can retire comfortably and never work again anywaymoneyaetna ceo bertolini how tech plays into the future of healthcareyahoo finance videocall of the week nows the time to buy chipotleyahoo financemary kay launches beauty industry first as thousands convene for us seminarpr newswirean obscure senate rule just put the gop healthcare bill in even bigger perilbusiness insiderone month after tim tebows ridiculed promotion he is on firebusiness insideraetna ceo bertolini why he pays his employees to sleepyahoo finance videostocks back off from record highsyahoo financetrump administration pulls health law help in  citiesassociated pressi tried the atkins on steroids diet for  months — and it made me feel invinciblebusiness insiderlebron james was reportedly devastated upon learning of kyrie irvings trade requestbusiness insideraetna ceo bertolini how his own accident and son’s cancer changed his journeyyahoo finance videowhat harlem thinks about whole foods coming to the neighborhoodyahoo financethe cia director just dropped some heavy hints that the us is looking into regime change in north koreabusiness insiderwhite house refuses to deny reports trump is considering pardoning himself over russia investigationwalt if trump and his lawyers are discussing this as the article suggests this leaves no doubt in my mind that laws have been violated and all this investigation is not just making too big a deal of issuesjoin the conversation   mic